node.title: Silver Ferns notch up first Quad Series win over South Africa at London
node.description: But the world champions allowed their rivals to take out the final quarter 16-11.
node.content: ["Rookie shooter Grace Nweke has shown her international potential, imposing her presence on South Africa during the Silver Ferns' 54-43 victory at the Northern Quad Series.", "NZ 54 (Nweke 30/32, Metuarau 15/16, Wilson 9/13)\u00a0South Africa 43 (Venter 31/36, Rademan 7/10, Burger 5/5)", "More to come"]
